{"tid":1482031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反暴力 撐經濟!","createTime":"2019-08-18T03:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T03:17:15.000Z","uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e09089afdaa23c93cee201dc47442bc82c09163","tid":1482031,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"斷人衣食猶如殺人父母<br />\n唔了解大國由又唱衰自己既國奸，大學生，政客，教授根本就係讀屎片，離哂大譜!<br />\n動亂分子想乘機推翻政權!<br />\n咁樣做，令所有既生活品物價暴升<br />\n你為左你既諗法同立場，影響到人地既生活，阻到人地飲咖啡，糖，做生意。值得咩??? 要民主要自由，鬥大聲就得咩? 有冇問過人地感受? 爭取自由同時，又影響人地自由，合邏輯咩? 點解要人地一定同意你? 民主咩? <br />\n<br />\n我問你呀! On9，正垃圾!<br />\n講咩法治? 所有野都喺法律入面寫得好清楚!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bl.uk/learning/histcitizen/campaignforabolition/sources/proslavery/proslaveryarticle/proslaveryarticle.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bl.uk%2Flearning%2Fhistcitizen%2Fcampaignforabolition%2Fsources%2Fproslavery%2Fproslaveryarticle%2Fproslaveryarticle.html&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=95b6b5c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bl.uk/learning/histcitizen/campaignforabolition/sources/proslavery/proslaveryarticle/proslaveryarticle.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/ethics/slavery/ethics/justifications.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fethics%2Fslavery%2Fethics%2Fjustifications.shtml&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a44e4aac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/ethics/slavery/ethics/justifications.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n因為奴隸係財產，唔係人! 所以唔需要人權!<br />\n有史以來就有奴隸! 不存在有問題! 冇奴隸經濟會變差，物價飛揚，工廠停產! 百業蕭條! 仲要損害他人財產，無恥!<br />\n<br />\n奴隸解放者可恥! 以平權為名 搞亂世界! <br />\n 建議聯署為奴隸制度平反! 反暴力! 撐經濟! </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e18670824b2fe154a9fe1a175fa3d7e8775a6b","tid":1482031,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime